  "description": "<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Mateo spominje svoj uzrast na španskom koristeći sledeću strukturu, i glagol <span class=\"highlighted-text\">tener</span> (\"imati\"):</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Tengo</span> + broj rečima + <span class=\"highlighted-text\">años</span>.</p>\n<p>Napomena, španske brojeve od 21 do 29 počinju sa <span class=\"highlighted-text\">veinti-</span>, praćenim odgovarajućim brojem. Primer:</p>\n<p>25 je <span class=\"highlighted-text\">veinticinco</span>. Ovo nastaje uklanjanjem <span class=\"highlighted-text\">e</span> i dodavanjem <span class=\"highlighted-text\">i</span> pre broja <span class=\"highlighted-text\">cinco</span>.</p>\n<p>Brojevi od 1 do 9 na španskom su:</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"center\">Broj</th>\n<th align=\"center\">Španski Izraz</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">1</td>\n<td align=\"center\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">uno</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">2</td>\n<td align=\"center\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">dos</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">3</td>\n<td align=\"center\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">tres</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">4</td>\n<td align=\"center\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">cuatro</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">5</td>\n<td align=\"center\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">cinco</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">6</td>\n<td align=\"center\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">seis</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">7</td>\n<td align=\"center\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">siete</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">8</td>\n<td align=\"center\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">ocho</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">9</td>\n<td align=\"center\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">nueve</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</section>",
  "instructions": "<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Slušaj zvuk/audio i odgovori na pitanje koje je ispod.</p>\n</section>",
  "explanation": "<section id=\"explanation\">\n<p>Usemi <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Tengo veinticinco años</span> znači da je Mateo star 25 godina.</p>\n<p>Zapamti da slovo <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ñ</span> u <span class=\"highlighted-text\">años</span> ima drugačiji zvuk.</p>\n</section>",
